  "detailed_description": "\"Silent Station\" is a social, psychological, multiplayer game based on the rules of the classic mafia, complemented by the features of setting death traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.poster.avif?t=1693218268\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.webm?t=1693218268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.mp4?t=1693218268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The rules are simple: there is a crew, there is a traitor.<br>The crew goal is to figure out the traitor and throw him out into space or complete all the tasks at the spaceship.<br><br>The traitor, on the other hand, can set death traps in advance or directly eliminate crew members.<br>(!) Block the door right in front of the victim's nose!<br>(!) Turn, initially peaceful crew members, into your monstermates!<br>(!) Hide bodies by breaking the spaceship lighting!<br>(!) Launch the self-destruct system!<br><br>All this awaits you at the \"Silent Station\"!",
  "about_the_game": "\"Silent Station\" is a social, psychological, multiplayer game based on the rules of the classic mafia, complemented by the features of setting death traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.poster.avif?t=1693218268\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.webm?t=1693218268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292980/extras/ef25cc73dc60b11b4468195efbb66e90.mp4?t=1693218268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The rules are simple: there is a crew, there is a traitor.<br>The crew goal is to figure out the traitor and throw him out into space or complete all the tasks at the spaceship.<br><br>The traitor, on the other hand, can set death traps in advance or directly eliminate crew members.<br>(!) Block the door right in front of the victim's nose!<br>(!) Turn, initially peaceful crew members, into your monstermates!<br>(!) Hide bodies by breaking the spaceship lighting!<br>(!) Launch the self-destruct system!<br><br>All this awaits you at the \"Silent Station\"!",
